      "content": "ugh my head just killed me. like literally out of nowhere it felt like someone hit me in the skull with a hammer or something. legit the worst pain ever for like a minute but it's mostly gone now, i just feel kinda weird and foggy. think i might just be dehydrated from studying all night? what should i do?",
